12:18.234 --> 12:19.833
the joke about the stormtrooper...
I can't... I can't joke?

12:19.833 --> 12:21.634
And of course the biggie:

12:22.634 --> 12:25.000
The Canadian/American War.

12:25.000 --> 12:27.267
Thank God that song's over.

12:27.267 --> 12:29.634
Who the hell was 
that old lady singing?

12:29.634 --> 12:33.034
Okay, you know that Neil Young
is my favorite musician.

12:33.034 --> 12:35.100
Right. Now, was that the same
old lady who played

12:35.100 --> 12:36.967
Archie Bunker's wife
in All in the Family,

12:36.967 --> 12:38.100
or just sound-alike?

12:38.100 --> 12:40.967
Neil Young is
a Canadian treasure.

12:40.967 --> 12:43.534
Do not make fun of Neil Young.

12:43.534 --> 12:45.434
Robin, I would
never make fun of

12:45.434 --> 12:48.100
a defenseless old lady with
vocal cord paralysis... ever.

12:48.100 --> 12:50.967
Oh, here we go. In public?
Really? In public?
Yeah, in public. I'll go there.

12:50.967 --> 12:53.467
What's the problem? Everything
I say...
We're gonna have a fight in public?

12:53.467 --> 12:54.534
I got it.

12:54.534 --> 12:56.534
I got it.
We e-mail them pictures

12:56.534 --> 12:58.467
reminding them
of each of these fights.

12:58.467 --> 13:00.434
You child.

13:01.434 --> 13:02.700
Here's how it goes down.

13:02.700 --> 13:03.668
They're at the diner...

13:03.668 --> 13:04.767
LILY:
First, rekindling

13:04.767 --> 13:06.567
<i>the Canadian-American debate,</i>

13:06.567 --> 13:08.667
<i>Ontario native Alan Thicke
stops by the table.</i>

13:08.667 --> 13:09.834
<i>TED & MARSHALL:
Whoa! Whoa!</i>

13:09.834 --> 13:11.734
Whoa-whoa-whoa!
Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!

13:11.734 --> 13:12.667
Alan Thicke?

13:12.667 --> 13:14.667
Oh, right.
Robin knew him

13:14.667 --> 13:15.634
back when she was a singer.

13:15.634 --> 13:17.367
Yeah, and they still
keep in touch.

13:17.367 --> 13:19.467
I already got his number
off her phone.

13:19.467 --> 13:21.967
Seriously... amateurs.

13:21.967 --> 13:23.967
<i>LILY:
So Alan Thicke restarts</i>

13:23.967 --> 13:24.934
<i>the Canada-U.S. fight.</i>

13:24.934 --> 13:26.634
<i>Right at that moment,</i>

13:26.634 --> 13:28.134
<i>Crazy Meg shows up.</i>

13:28.134 --> 13:32.200
<i>Then, a stormtrooper happens
to walk by the window.</i>

13:32.200 --> 13:34.233
<i>And just when they can't take
anything more,</i>

13:34.233 --> 13:35.600
<i>a busboy walks by</i>

13:35.600 --> 13:37.068
<i>with a tray full of what?</i>

13:37.068 --> 13:39.934
<i>Dirty dishes.</i>

13:41.200 --> 13:42.333
