restraining order thing.

19:08.468 --> 19:10.334
Uh, hi.

19:10.334 --> 19:12.434
Whoa, is that a stormtrooper?

19:12.434 --> 19:14.667
That's not a stormtr...
You want to get out of here?

19:14.667 --> 19:16.201
Yeah.

19:16.201 --> 19:18.468
See you guys.
Okay.

19:18.468 --> 19:19.500
See you, Alan.

19:19.500 --> 19:21.101
(chuckling)

19:21.101 --> 19:22.967
So you still on 73rd Street?

19:22.967 --> 19:26.001
How do you know that?

19:26.800 --> 19:28.567
Getting back together

19:28.567 --> 19:30.734
as friends... I like that.

19:30.734 --> 19:32.734
One more for the road?

19:39.501 --> 19:41.300
And, I mean, who knows?

19:41.300 --> 19:43.000
Maybe, when,
like, you turn 40,

19:43.000 --> 19:44.234
if you haven't found anyone...

19:44.234 --> 19:45.767
Oh, I already have
that deal with Ted.

19:45.767 --> 19:48.734
Oh, right. Stupid.

19:48.734 --> 19:50.467
Well, maybe when you turn 39,

19:50.467 --> 19:51.801
if you haven't
found anyone...

19:51.801 --> 19:54.467
<i>It turns out
that they really did</i>

19:54.467 --> 19:56.834
<i>just need to let things
run their course.</i>

19:58.100 --> 19:59.334
So, uh, how's Barney doing?

19:59.334 --> 20:00.734
He's okay, I think.

